Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.23,0:00:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,情况真是糟糕透了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This could not have gone more wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎到底是怎么了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.34,0:00:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们花了几个月的时间过你的生活\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We've spent a couple of months living your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.19,0:00:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎充满冒险和胜利\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Adventures and victories.
