Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.78,0:03:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎下次 ‎找个不那么危险的地方撒尿 好吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Next time, find somewhere less dangerous to pee, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎好吧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:20.38,特效,,0,0,0,,{\bord0.1\blur3\fn华文中宋\fs33\fscx95\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HDC&\3a&HDC&\t(20,658,\1a&H00&,\3a&H96&)\t(4274,5359,\1a&HC0&,\3a&HC0&)\pos(192,122.8)\3c&H000000&}‎‎四周前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.28,0:03:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这不是我的错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This isn't my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.61,0:03:25.49,Default,,0,0,0,,‎很公平 这次是我的错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Quite fair. This one's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎-我会弥补过失的  -‎靠你自己吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- I will make it right. - On your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们寡不敌众 ‎他们比我们高大\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We're outnumbered, they're bigger than us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去怒气冲冲的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and they look quite annoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.19,0:03:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你最好蹲下来\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You may want to crouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.57,0:04:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你瞧\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,他们从哪弄来的这个\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Where did they get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.28,0:04:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许出自布勒伊拉的城堡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Perhaps it washed out of the castle at Braila.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.69,Default,,0,0,0,,‎难怪这些家伙这么生气\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No wonder these creatures were so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.28,0:04:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我们打扰了他们的祈祷\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}We disturbed them while they were praying to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:33.38,特效,,0,0,0,,{\bord0.1\blur3\fn华文中宋\fs33\fscx95\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HDC&\3a&HDC&\t(5,658,\1a&H00&,\3a&H96&)\pos(192,122.8)\3c&H000000&}‎‎‎三周前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.53,0:05:24.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这是魔咒\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.03,0:05:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,-‎依靠杀人来唤醒  -‎什么魔咒\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Murder wakes it up. - What kind of spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,‎起死回生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Resurrection.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.11,0:05:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这办法根本没用 ‎少了东西\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It wouldn't have worked. It's missing parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎但他原本要杀了这些人来试手\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he would have killed these people to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.53,0:05:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-‎少了什么东西  -一道‎印记 ‎算是一种神奇的密码\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- And the other thing? - A sigil. Sort of a magical code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.53,0:05:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,‎上面会有他\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It will have the name of the person
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.32,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,想要复活的人的名字\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}he was trying to bring back from the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.15,0:05:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,‎让我猜猜看\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, let me guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.23,0:05:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎破译出来就是弗拉德·德古拉·特佩斯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It decodes as Vlad Dracula Tepes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,‎为什么有人会这样做\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Why the fuck would anyone do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你们会这样做吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Would you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.15,0:05:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,‎没错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.03,0:05:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊 我真是快疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God, this is getting on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.57,0:06:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,真希望我能杀你两次\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I wish I could fucking kill you twice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:10.71,特效,,0,0,0,,{\pos(192,191)\bord0.1\blur3\fn华文中宋\fs33\fscx95\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HDC&\3a&HDC&\t(16,642,0.6,\1a&H00&,\3a&H96&)\t(3228,4395,1.5,\1a&HE0&,\3a&HE0&)}‎‎两周前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎妈的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.53,0:06:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-‎你刚刚说什么  -‎我说"妈的" 不行吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- What did you just say? - I said, "shit," okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.48,0:06:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎行啊 只是你从来不骂人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Yes, it's just that you never, you know, curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.78,0:06:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我从来没骂过人 后来发生了这些事\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I never used to, and then all this happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,然后遇到了你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And then you happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.69,0:06:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎‎-我吗  -没错 就是你\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}- Me? - Yes, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.82,0:06:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我本来很有礼貌\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I was nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.53,0:06:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后我遇到了你 现在我像你一样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And then I met you, and now I'm like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.69,0:06:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,所以 是我的错吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, so it's my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.53,0:06:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,‎都是你的错\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}It's all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.03,0:06:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你把我变成了这样\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You did this to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我发现你他妈在坟墓里变成了雕像\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I found you turned into a statue in a fucking tomb!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.94,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,‎然后你缠上我\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And climbed all over me,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.53,0:06:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,‎从那一刻起 一切都糟透了 ‎而且…\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and since that moment everything has been shit and...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我他妈的在说话呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I am fucking talking here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.53,0:07:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你让我学会了骂人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And you turned me into someone who says "shit."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.78,0:07:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,‎去你妈的傻逼大混球\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Fuckity shit hairy arse-warts giant slimy balls!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,‎妈的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:26.63,特效,,0,0,0,,‎{\bord0.1\blur3\fn华文中宋\fs33\fscx95\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HDC&\3a&HDC&\t(10,468,\1a&H00&,\3a&H96&)\t(4347,5015,\1a&HE9&,\3a&HE9&)\pos(192,122.8)\3c&H000000&}‎‎一周前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.76,0:07:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,‎活人献祭真的死灰复燃了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Human sacrifice really is back in fashion.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.61,0:07:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这又是为了德古拉伯爵吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Do we think this is about Dracula again?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.02,0:07:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我觉得 这些人只不过在发疯\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I think these people are just out of their minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.76,0:07:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎所以我们不会试着跟他们讲道理\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And so we're not going to try and reason with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.38,0:08:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎不\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.93,0:08:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他们要杀害孩子\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}They were going to murder children.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.49,0:08:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎孩子们 趴下 快点\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Kids, lay down flat. Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那是什么玩意\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's that thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.09,0:09:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我只在书上看过画像\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I've only seen drawings in books.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他有很多名字\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He has a lot of names.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他通常被称为镰刀死神\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Most often, he's called the Grim Reaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.93,0:09:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,或者就叫死神\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Or just Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.98,0:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他真的是死神吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's actually Death?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.63,0:09:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我是说 死神就长这样吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I mean, this is what Death looks like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.68,0:09:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,‎因为我希望更好看些\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Because I was hoping for something nicer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,‎才不是呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.80,0:10:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎只是远古时代的人\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Just people from an earlier time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.01,0:10:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎想弄清楚他们看到的景象\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}trying to understand what they were seeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,‎有些元素生物只以自然界的东西为食\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}There are elemental beings that just feed on things in nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,‎他不是死神 他只是吞噬死亡\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's not Death. He just eats death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.97,0:10:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,‎那你觉得这只是他的神殿吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}So this is just a shrine to him, you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人们仍然认为这是死神本人吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}People who still think this is Death itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎人们来此朝拜\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Paying tribute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,‎也许希望他能让德古拉伯爵起死回生\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Maybe in the hope that he can give Dracula back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.30,0:10:25.84,Default,,0,0,0,,‎别误会我的意思\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Don't get me wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他可以夺人性命\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}He's supposed to be lethal.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.47,0:10:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,‎却没有深入地狱\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}But he's not the sort of power who can reach into Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.76,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让人复活的力量\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}and pull someone out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.13,0:10:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,‎全世界都疯了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}The whole world's gone crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.09,0:10:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,‎这块大石头呢\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}And this big stone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,‎石板\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Flagstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.05,0:10:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,‎一定是从某个城镇广场上撬来的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Must have been prized up from a town square somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.55,0:10:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎最近哪个地方的广场上有石板\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}What's the nearest place that would have flagstones in their square?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.45,0:10:56.45,特效,,0,0,0,,‎{\bord0.1\blur3\fn华文中宋\fs33\fscx95\b0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&HDC&\3a&HDC&\t(8,1635,0.8,\1a&H00&,\3a&H96&)\t(4679,5972,\1a&He0&,\3a&HE0&)\pos(192,122.8)\3c&H000000&}‎‎今晚
