Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真的越来越难对付了\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}This is getting harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,‎真的吗\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,‎我没注意到\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}I hadn't noticed over the sound
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,‎全身的肌肉和骨头都在吱嘎作响\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}of all my muscles and bones screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.55,0:13:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,‎天啊\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.18,0:13:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,‎你会活下去的\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}You'll live.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.88,0:13:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,‎天啊 但愿如此\N{\c&H62a8eb&\fs13}God, I hope so.
